OL,3,CBeckie Ramsay 'elated' after child
OL,4,Cwater campaign safety success
OL,6,FA campaigner says she is "elated"
OL,7,Fafter the introduction of water safety
OL,8,Fon the national curriculum - hoping
OL,9,Fthe lessons should "help prevent
OL,10,Ffuture tragedies".
OL,12,FBeckie Ramsay's son Dylan, 13, a fit
OL,13,Fand strong swimmer, died within three
OL,14,Fminutes of entering water at Hilltop
OL,15,FQuarry in Whittle-le-Woods, close to
OL,16,Fhis home in .
OL,18,FHe had gone to cool down, but drowned
OL,19,Fafter suffering cold water shock.
