OL,3,CBeckie Ramsay 'elated' after child
OL,4,Cwater campaign safety success
OL,6,FThe government set out its '' in July
OL,7,F2023 which featured a section on
OL,8,Fswimming and water safety being
OL,9,Fincluded in the primary PE national
OL,10,Fcurriculum.
OL,12,FIt praised the "important
OL,13,Fcontribution" made by campaigners
OL,14,Fincluding Beckie for raising awareness
OL,15,Fand providing opportunities to teach
OL,16,Fpupils the "vital life skill".
OL,18,FReacting to the announcement Beckie
OL,19,Fsaid: "I'm absolutely elated. I don't
OL,20,Fthink I ever believed this day would
OL,21,Fever truly come.
