OL,3,CBeckie Ramsay 'elated' after child
OL,4,Cwater campaign safety success
OL,6,F"I'm going nowhere, I'm going to
OL,7,Fcontinue doing what I'm doing but also
OL,8,Fbroaden my horizons.
OL,10,F"Look at water safety equipment and
OL,11,Fcontinue to lobby parliament. This is
OL,12,Fjust the start."
OL,14,FOn average, 400 people drown in the UK
OL,15,Feach year and another 200 people take
OL,16,Ftheir own lives in water, according to
OL,17,Fthe National Water Safety Forum.
