OL,3,CBeckie Ramsay 'elated' after child
OL,4,Cwater campaign safety success
OL,6,FBeckie said: "If Dylan could drown, he
OL,7,Fwas 13 he was fit he was healthy, he
OL,8,Fwas a good swimmer, if this could
OL,9,Fhappen to Dylan this could happen to
OL,10,Fanyone.
OL,12,F"I couldn't sit back and do nothing.
OL,14,F"I'd be happy with a one hour lesson
OL,15,Fonce a year to start off with."
OL,17,FBeckie spends time traveling the
OL,18,Fcountry to deliver her message about
OL,19,FDylan to schools, colleges, emergency
OL,20,Fservices and workplaces.
